t9129: Make test find any UTF-8 locale

Commit 16fc08e2d86dad152194829d21bc55b2ef0c8fb1 introduced a
test that failed if the hardcoded en_US.UTF-8 locale was not
installed.

If no UTF-8 locale is found, skip the tests.
---

